  "summary": "Email typography: H1 28px/36px Nunito Sans ExtraBold/Bold; H2 22px/30px Bold; H3 18px/26px Bold/SemiBold; Body 16px/24px Regular (min); Secondary 14px/21px sparing; Footnote 12px/18px small & separate."
